name: Dwayne Johnson Dating Simulator
description:
Sometimes high school can be an awkward place where many people develop their identities in a confusing and excruciatingly long process. That's where we find ourselves in the Dwayne Johnson Dating Simulator. In a world where one Dwayne Johnson wasn't enough, we get to meet THREE Dwayne Johnsons, each with their own personal quirks, achievements, aspirations, and insecurities. How will you get through a day with this cooky cast of characters? Why don't you see for yourself?

And who knows, you may be surprised...
